# V5.0: confidence calibration table — must be tracked so daemon on the
# VM picks up the latest calibration after each weekly refit. Small JSON
# (~9KB), no secrets, regenerated by v4/calibrate_confidence.py.
!v4/confidence_calibration.json
# V5.0.2 dashboard data — auto-generated by scripts/build_trade_history.py,
# served by GitHub Pages from /docs. Must be tracked so the published site
# stays in sync with the latest closed trades.
!docs/data/
!docs/data/*.json

